Depending on the update that you make, you might need to restart the  server after you use the  POST method to update the HA configuration. 
You can restart the  server by using the  POST method with the following  configuration URI:http://<admin-endpoint-IP:Port>/ima/v1/service/restartProvide configuration data in the payload of the POST method by using the following schema.  Ensure that capitalization and double quotation marks are used as shown.
{    
  "Service": "Server" 

}
